Class InstalledDataConfiguration

java.lang.Object
  gov.nasa.worldwind.util.InstalledDataConfiguration

public class InstalledDataConfiguration
extends Object

An utility class for transforming an installed data "data descriptor" configuration document to a standard Layer or ElevationModel configuration document.
